<title>Boolean Methods</title>
<p>
<idx><h>boolean</h></idx>
<idx><h>method</h><h>boolean</h></idx>
Methods can return <c>boolean</c> values, just like any other type, which is often convenient for hiding tests inside methods.
For example:
</p>

